item.title: About
item.author: contact@philanatidae.com (Philanatidae)
item.description: Hello! I’m Philanatidae, Phil for short. I’m a full-time electrical engineer who is a hobbiest computer programmer. I have two projects I am actively working on. One is a game written in C# with FNA that I have been working on with a friend since August 2019. The other is a game engine that I am writing games alongside with to drive its development and architecture.
